        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Freedom for Families Act</b></p> <p>This bill modifies requirements for health savings accounts (HSAs) to (1) exclude from gross income HSA distributions paid or distributed during a period of qualified caregiving, (2) allow participation in an HSA without enrollment in a high deductible health plan, and (3) increase the contribution limit for HSAs. </p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
